    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>the way you said \"make the world fit your brokenness\"... that's kind of what i mean. the struggle is just endless. i feel like i'm running a race with no finish line and everyone is just waiting for me to trip so they can tell me i shouldn't have been running in the first place. i just don't see the point in continuing the effort if the outcome is always just more exhaustion and more pain. it's like, why bother?",
